precis:
Amendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS increasing the percentage of
foreign property that may be held, without the application of the penalty
tax under Part XI of the Act, by certain trusts, corporations and
partnerships in which entities subject to Part XI of the Act have an
interest.
